            "severity": "major",
            "rationale": "Reviewer's F13 cited DECISIONS.md:10-22 (single placeholder ADR-001 'Use JSON-LD Deterministic Service Template' dated '[TODAY]' with template-generic prose). Critic confirmed verbatim and enumerated the resolved decisions that are undocumented: seven OEDs in SPEC sec 27 (1638-1646), the CCO version pin, the iao: and cco: namespace decisions, the 5-layer vs 3-layer reconciliation, the v0.3 -> v0.4 reframing, and the realist-anchoring decision. CLAUDE.md sec 5 step 3 mandates session-start review of DECISIONS.md; the contract cannot be satisfied.",
