            "resolution": "accept_reviewer",
            "severity": "advisory",
            "rationale": "Reviewer's F18 noted both files are untracked, not referenced by SPEC sec 4.1, ARCHITECTURE.md, ROADMAP.md, or any FR/NFR, and state.jsonld's @context (https://fnsr.example/context.jsonld) does not resolve. Critic confirmed and added that the daemon orchestrates the very subagents acting on this spec \u00e2\u20ac\u201d the audit trail that gates spec evolution is itself out-of-spec. If in-scope, place in the layer model and confine non-deterministic timestamp generation to an adapter; if out-of-scope, exclude explicitly in sec 3.2.",
            "trace": {
